<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Surely every man walks about like a shadow.</para>

<para style="q1">Surely everyone hurries about</para>

<para style="q1">to accumulate riches although they do not know who will receive them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Now, Lord, for what am I waiting?</para>

<para style="q1">You are my only hope.</para>
